  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Akimichi.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Akimichi Clan, Level 4+</p><p>You have undergone rigorous training to condition your body to absorb nutrition from anything. You gain the following benefits;</p><p>• When you would eat a consumable, such as a Blood Pill, Military Ration Pill, or any other ingestible consumable item, you regain 1d4 calories. You can regain calories this way twice per short rest.</p><p>• You have resistance to the Poisoned and Weakened Condition rolling advantage on all saving throws and checks made to resist such conditions.</p><p>• Poison damage you take from the Envenomed condition is reduced by 1 step (D6&gt;D4</p><p>• You gain advantage on skill checks and Saving throws to resist environmental Hazards &amp; Conditions</p>",
